race.description: Central Coast Aqua Park Maiden Plate
race.comment: The well-related VASALA (2) (half to G1 winner Spright) was heavily supported at Kembla Grange on debut but just found one better on that occasion. Will have derived benefit from that race day experience and where there's smoke there's fire. Looks the one they all have to run down. MAREBELLO (1) has been right there in all three starts to date and has since joined the champion Waller yard. Looms as the main danger. GARRIX (4) defied expectations placing in town when resuming and will have come on with that run now in the locker. Top-three candidate. ROYAL CHIC (12) also hails from a handy family (half to G1 winner Royal Merchant) and will be ready to peak now third-up from the break. In the mix. LIKE ANYTHING (11) rounds out the selections.
